WildyScape thread in progress
Welcome to WildyScape this is my first ever Release, its based of Demise pking v5. Some of the features of WildyScape have never been seen by another humon being. This isent a server you can download and instantly host it still need another few days of solid coding. Im gona Keep this Short and sweet.
source and client: [url=http://www.megaupload.com/?d=HSLAFDXO]http://www.megaupload.com/?d=HSLAFDXO[/url] [url=http://www.megaupload.com/?d=HSLAFDXO]http://www.megaupload.com/?d=HSLAFDXO[/url] sorry about wait.
-Full wilderness BountyHunter. -Targets. -Chaotics. -Summoning. -pkp Exchange. -Hiscores. -Sol. -BountyHunter locate. -Corp -Spirit shields. -525 emotes. -525 Interfaces. -Much much more..
Now for what you all have been waiting for. DONT GO HATIN!
